The **Senior Citizen Savings Scheme (SCSS)** is a government-backed scheme exclusively for senior citizens (60+) offering 8.2% p.a. interest paid quarterly, making it ideal for regular income in retirement. Maximum deposit is ₹30 lakh per individual. The scheme has a 5-year tenure, extendable by 3 years. Interest qualifies for a ₹50,000 deduction under Section 80TTB.
